(330, 1, '2019-02-01 06:50:49', '2019-02-01 06:50:49', '<!-- wp:image {"id":94,"align":"right","width":445,"height":312,"className":"b99f3995a-4ce2-41af-bc35-09758b21f379","blockOpts":{"id":"99f3995a-4ce2-41af-bc35-09758b21f379"}} -->\n<div class="wp-block-image b99f3995a-4ce2-41af-bc35-09758b21f379"><figure class="alignright is-resized"><img src="http://wp.deansluyter.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/full-image.php-Version-3.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-94" width="445" height="312"/><figcaption>Dean walking the walk and talking the talk.</figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"className":"bfe866b73-c143-49bf-aaf3-d5798d23d9ba","blockOpts":{"id":"fe866b73-c143-49bf-aaf3-d5798d23d9ba"}} -->\n<h2 class="bfe866b73-c143-49bf-aaf3-d5798d23d9ba">Biography</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"b0b9d8ca2-cb95-4c7a-b90f-3fbfc4ee8bc0","blockOpts":{"id":"0b9d8ca2-cb95-4c7a-b90f-3fbfc4ee8bc0"}} -->\n<p class="b0b9d8ca2-cb95-4c7a-b90f-3fbfc4ee8bc0">Award-winning author Dean Sluyter (pronounced "slighter") has taught natural methods of meditation and awakening since 1970. His five highly acclaimed books include the back-to-back Amazon #1 stress-management bestsellers Natural Meditation and Fear Less: Living Beyond Fear, Anxiety, Anger, and Addiction. Dean gives talks, workshops, and retreats throughout the United States and beyond, from Ivy League colleges to maximum-security prisons. His media appearances have included National Public Radio, The New York Times, New York Magazine, Coast to Coast AM, The Dr. Oz Show, and O, The Oprah Magazine.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":93,"align":"left","width":77,"height":88,"className":"be332a63f-24ac-40e0-9024-f60f0c5e4a3e","blockOpts":{"id":"e332a63f-24ac-40e0-9024-f60f0c5e4a3e"}} -->\n<div class="wp-block-image be332a63f-24ac-40e0-9024-f60f0c5e4a3e"><figure class="alignleft is-resized"><img src="http://wp.deansluyter.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Featured-In-2-890x1024.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-93" width="77" height="88"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"b485b6bed-9536-4452-9ba8-85d5d1965abf","blockOpts":{"id":"485b6bed-9536-4452-9ba8-85d5d1965abf"}} -->\n<p class="b485b6bed-9536-4452-9ba8-85d5d1965abf">A grateful student of&nbsp;Eastern and Western sages&nbsp;in several traditions, Dean has completed numerous pilgrimages and retreats in India, Tibet, Nepal, and the West. He is known for conveying authentic teachings in forms that are relaxed, accessible, and down-to-earth. When not writing or teaching, he <a href="http://deansluyter.com/content/narration"><strong>narrates audiobooks</strong></a>, administers the&nbsp;<a href="http://awakeningprisonart.com/"><strong>Awakening Prison Art</strong></a>&nbsp;project, makes music, and happily tools around the streets of Santa Monica on his Vespa.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"b44d63c46-450e-4c75-a434-46b09891bf1f","blockOpts":{"id":"44d63c46-450e-4c75-a434-46b09891bf1f"}} -->\n<p class="b44d63c46-450e-4c75-a434-46b09891bf1f">Dean lived in New Jersey for 33 years, where he&nbsp;developed&nbsp;<a href="http://deansluyter.com/content/meditation-classroom"><strong>classroom meditation</strong></a>&nbsp;programs at The Pingry School and worked with inmates at Northern State Prison. He is now on the faculty of the West Coast Writers Conferences and&nbsp;is married to documentary filmmaker&nbsp;<strong><a href="http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0503502/?ref_=fn_al_nm_1">Yaffa Lerea</a></strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":99,"align":"right","width":172,"height":222,"className":"bcd909103-2afc-4fa8-8d4d-8474437a996a","blockOpts":{"id":"cd909103-2afc-4fa8-8d4d-8474437a996a"}} -->\n<div class="wp-block-image bcd909103-2afc-4fa8-8d4d-8474437a996a"><figure class="alignright is-resized"><img src="http://wp.deansluyter.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Screenshot-2018-11-23-22.24.21.png" alt="" class="wp-image-99" width="172" height="222"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3,"className":"b912ac700-33ed-435b-8bba-3501b2dd5c54","blockOpts":{"id":"912ac700-33ed-435b-8bba-3501b2dd5c54"}} -->\n<h3 class="b912ac700-33ed-435b-8bba-3501b2dd5c54">To Book Dean for Your Next Event</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"b5c1f5cd8-2dbd-4fc2-b557-03fba6dd739c","blockOpts":{"id":"5c1f5cd8-2dbd-4fc2-b557-03fba6dd739c"}} -->\n<p class="b5c1f5cd8-2dbd-4fc2-b557-03fba6dd739c">Contact&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@deansluyter.com?subject=Event%20Inquiry"><strong>info@deansluyter.com</strong></a>. For more information, view Dean\'s&nbsp;<a href="https://adobeindd.com/view/publications/7bcd5c35-be63-4641-80c4-a61082fd4672/1/publication-web-resources/pdf/Sluyter_1-Sheet_Nov_2018.pdf"><strong>1-sheet</strong></a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"className":"bbb8d4e82-416f-44e0-81e3-889b120dc12e","blockOpts":{"id":"bb8d4e82-416f-44e0-81e3-889b120dc12e"}} -->\n<h2 class="bbb8d4e82-416f-44e0-81e3-889b120dc12e"><strong>TESTIMONIALS</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote {"className":"ba669b967-eac1-4e25-b994-742f8a2719fa","blockOpts":{"id":"a669b967-eac1-4e25-b994-742f8a2719fa"}} -->\n<blockquote class="wp-block-quote ba669b967-eac1-4e25-b994-742f8a2719fa"><p>"The laid-back, down-to-earth approach made meditation appealing and easy, even for complete novices.&nbsp;Deans presentation was of tremendous value in supporting our view of meditations benefits for our associates, both personal and professional."<br></p><cite><em>Haley Akin, Senior Health &amp; Wellness Specialist,&nbsp;<strong>Garmin International</strong></em></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":96,"align":"right","width":281,"height":216,"className":"b64bb50c1-9b29-4466-8c5b-31bbd0d5b24d","blockOpts":{"id":"64bb50c1-9b29-4466-8c5b-31bbd0d5b24d"}} -->\n<div class="wp-block-image b64bb50c1-9b29-4466-8c5b-31bbd0d5b24d"><figure class="alignright is-resized"><img src="http://wp.deansluyter.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_0866-crop-more_0.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-96" width="281" height="216"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote {"className":"b71761363-a95b-4a51-8a3d-0729a365361b","blockOpts":{"id":"71761363-a95b-4a51-8a3d-0729a365361b"}} -->\n<blockquote class="wp-block-quote b71761363-a95b-4a51-8a3d-0729a365361b"><p>"We loved having you at Timber Creek, and we\'re most grateful for what you offered. The guests soaked it up and loved your natural, genuine style. We\'re elated you could come and look forward to a future visit."<br><em></em></p><cite><em>Tom Jacobs, Director,&nbsp;<strong>Timber Creek Retreat House</strong></em></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote {"className":"bb2f4cc2b-25ca-4929-9cdf-dfed599732d8","blockOpts":{"id":"b2f4cc2b-25ca-4929-9cdf-dfed599732d8"}} -->\n<blockquote class="wp-block-quote bb2f4cc2b-25ca-4929-9cdf-dfed599732d8"><p>"What a pleasure to host Dean for his Natural Meditation workshop! Dean speaks with clarity and ease from his own years of experience with meditation, so students are naturally engaged. He made a connection with everyone in the room  from seasoned yogis to my skeptical 70-year-old mother!"<em></em>&nbsp;</p><cite><em>Jamie Rye, owner,&nbsp;<strong>One Tree Yoga,&nbsp;</strong>Omaha</em></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":95,"align":"right","width":231,"height":154,"className":"bfe40ec4e-6f99-4d84-9c2f-c08364e07931","blockOpts":{"id":"fe40ec4e-6f99-4d84-9c2f-c08364e07931"}} -->\n<div class="wp-block-image bfe40ec4e-6f99-4d84-9c2f-c08364e07931"><figure class="alignright is-resized"><img src="http://wp.deansluyter.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Garmin.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-95" width="231" height="154"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote {"className":"bc8397f01-e4cc-4706-8786-829d40a11fa7","blockOpts":{"id":"c8397f01-e4cc-4706-8786-829d40a11fa7"}} -->\n<blockquote class="wp-block-quote bc8397f01-e4cc-4706-8786-829d40a11fa7"><p>"Dean\'s methodology is simple and easy to grasp. He is practical in his teachings and is a presenter who is easy to warm up to."&nbsp;</p><cite><em>Jos Falla, Guatemala Education Officer,&nbsp;<strong>Young Presidents\' Organization</strong></em></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote {"className":"b8f034553-7497-4858-bd00-508d5ea7f094","blockOpts":{"id":"8f034553-7497-4858-bd00-508d5ea7f094"}} -->\n<blockquote class="wp-block-quote b8f034553-7497-4858-bd00-508d5ea7f094"><p>"You made killers peaceful."</p><cite><em>Meditation Program Participant,&nbsp;<strong>Northern State Prison,&nbsp;</strong>Newark, NJ</em></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"className":"b51ffbc59-473b-4837-bcb0-d3262a75aebb","blockOpts":{"id":"51ffbc59-473b-4837-bcb0-d3262a75aebb"}} -->\n<h2 class="b51ffbc59-473b-4837-bcb0-d3262a75aebb">Teachers</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":98,"align":"right","width":341,"height":256,"className":"bf8a3ee13-3fe1-4750-91cb-0ac61845260a","blockOpts":{"id":"f8a3ee13-3fe1-4750-91cb-0ac61845260a"}} -->\n<div class="wp-block-image bf8a3ee13-3fe1-4750-91cb-0ac61845260a"><figure class="alignright is-resized"><img src="http://wp.deansluyter.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Rupert-Mooji-Charles-MMY_1-1024x768.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-98" width="341" height="256"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"b2e8936ee-9163-46ee-8011-a638daf14466","blockOpts":{"id":"2e8936ee-9163-46ee-8011-a638daf14466"}} -->\n<p class="b2e8936ee-9163-46ee-8011-a638daf14466">Dean is deeply grateful to the many teachers who have guided him over the years, representing methods and traditions including Advaita Vedanta, Bhakti Yoga, Transcendental Meditation, Umbanda, and Vajrayana Buddhism. Teachers whose personal guidance has been especially important include Maharishi Mahesh Yogi, Charles Genoud, Mooji, and Rupert Spira.</p>\n<!-- /wp:pa