 appealing and easy, even for complete novices.Deans presentation was of tremendous value in supporting our view of meditations benefits for our associates, both personal and professional."<br><em>Haley Akin, Senior Health &amp; Wellness Specialist,<strong>Garmin International</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":" b835d64c9-bc37-49f3-b1a9-43cc42bd0e4b ","blockOpts":{"id":"835d64c9-bc37-49f3-b1a9-43cc42bd0e4b"}} -->\n<p class=" b835d64c9-bc37-49f3-b1a9-43cc42bd0e4b ">"We loved having you at Timber Creek, and we\'re most grateful for what you offered. The guests soaked it up and loved your natural, genuine style. We\'re elated you could come and look forward to a future visit."<br><em>Tom Jacobs, Director,<strong>Timber Creek Retreat House</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":" be315014a-1099-4dd4-b631-5ba08f64077a ","blockOpts":{"id":"e315014a-1099-4dd4-b631-5ba08f64077a"}} -->\n<p class=" be315014a-1099-4dd4-b631-5ba08f64077a ">"What a pleasure to host Dean for his Natural Meditation workshop! Dean speaks with clarity and ease from his own years of experience with meditation, so students are naturally engaged. He made a connection with everyone in the room  from seasoned yogis to my skeptical 70-year-old mother!"<br><em>Jamie Rye, owner,<strong>One Tree Yoga,</strong>Omaha</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":" bae481728-32ff-47d1-8026-13f027c2598a ","blockOpts":{"id":"ae481728-32ff-47d1-8026-13f027c2598a"}} -->\n<p class=" bae481728-32ff-47d1-8026-13f027c2598a ">"Dean\'s methodology is simple and easy to grasp. He is practical in his teachings and is a presenter who is easy to warm up to."<br><em>Jos Falla, Guatemala Education Officer,<strong>Young Presidents\' Organization</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":" b8d087d42-5188-4c61-97ce-5147d756a70d ","blockOpts":{"id":"8d087d42-5188-4c61-97ce-5147d756a70d"}} -->\n<p class=" b8d087d42-5188-4c61-97ce-5147d756a70d ">"You made killers peaceful."<br><em>Meditation Program Participant,<strong>Northern State Prison,</strong>Newark, NJ</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":358,"align":"right","width":455,"height":341,"className":"bb76c3cee-fe0f-4b0d-8dc0-fbcba90575f0","blockOpts":{"id":"b76c3cee-fe0f-4b0d-8dc0-fbcba90575f0"}} -->\n<div class="wp-block-image bb76c3cee-fe0f-4b0d-8dc0-fbcba90575f0"><figure class="alignright is-resized"><img src="http://wp.deansluyter.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Rupert-Mooji-Charles-MMY_1-1024x768.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-358" width="455" height="341"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3,"className":"b53670fef-33fd-4a08-9fea-52bd91cb38f1","blockOpts":{"id":"53670fef-33fd-4a08-9fea-52bd91cb38f1"}} -->\n<h3 class="b53670fef-33fd-4a08-9fea-52bd91cb38f1">Teachers</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"b6bd96326-1d98-4a39-8ddf-7770e1a4a15c","blockOpts":{"id":"6bd96326-1d98-4a39-8ddf-7770e1a4a15c"}} -->\n<p class="b6bd96326-1d98-4a39-8ddf-7770e1a4a15c">Dean is deeply grateful to the many teachers who have guided him over the years, representing methods and traditions including Advaita Vedanta, Bhakti Yoga, Transcendental Meditation, Umbanda, and Vajrayana Buddhism. Teachers whose personal guidance has been especially important include Maharishi Mahesh Yogi, Charles Genoud, Mooji, and Rupert Spira.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Welcome to DeanSluyter.com!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '284-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-02-10 23:43:26', '2019-02-10 23:43:26', '', 284, 'http://wp.deansluyter.com/content/284-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ;
