(646, 2, '2019-05-21 00:53:23', '2019-05-21 00:53:23', '<!-- wp:image {"id":344,"align":"right","width":414,"height":292,"className":"b74e74c7b-1e24-43be-99b4-af40c135322f"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-image b74e74c7b-1e24-43be-99b4-af40c135322f"><figure class="alignright is-resized"><img src="http://wp.deansluyter.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/full-image.php-Version-3.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-344" width="414" height="292"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"b0911ebd6-5aea-4b2d-bbc6-5ecdb53bec33"} -->\n<p class="b0911ebd6-5aea-4b2d-bbc6-5ecdb53bec33">Award-winning author Dean Sluyter (pronounced&nbsp;<em>"slighter"</em>) has taught natural methods of meditation and awakening since 1970. His five highly acclaimed books include the back-to-back Amazon #1 stress-management bestsellers&nbsp;<em><strong><a href="http://deansluyter.com/content/natural-meditation">Natural Meditation</a></strong></em>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong><em><a href="http://deansluyter.com/content/fear-less">Fear Less: Living Beyond Fear, Anxiety, Anger, and Addiction</a></em></strong>. Dean&nbsp;gives talks, workshops, and retreats throughout the United States and beyond, from Ivy League colleges to maximum-security prisons. His media appearances have included National Public Radio,&nbsp;The New York Times, New York Magazine, Coast to Coast AM, The Dr. Oz Show, and O, The Oprah Magazine.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":343,"align":"left","width":263,"height":302,"className":"bc4d4c8fb-7838-4123-9083-d34b1c1fbed8"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-image bc4d4c8fb-7838-4123-9083-d34b1c1fbed8"><figure class="alignleft is-resized"><img src="http://wp.deansluyter.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Featured-In-2-890x1024.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-343" width="263" height="302"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"b2adcfa86-b83d-4f18-abec-c2db4314f49d"} -->\n<p class="b2adcfa86-b83d-4f18-abec-c2db4314f49d">A grateful student of&nbsp;Eastern and Western sages&nbsp;in several traditions, Dean has completed numerous pilgrimages and retreats in India, Tibet, Nepal, and the West. He is known for conveying authentic teachings in forms that are relaxed, accessible, and down-to-earth. When not writing or teaching, he&nbsp;<a href="http://deansluyter.com/content/narration"><strong>narrates audiobooks</strong></a>, administers the<a href="http://awakeningprisonart.com/"><strong>Awakening Prison Art</strong></a>&nbsp;project, makes music, and happily tools around the streets of Santa Monica on his Vespa.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"b64149f40-fe49-404d-bc41-c33824676c71"} -->\n<p class="b64149f40-fe49-404d-bc41-c33824676c71">Dean lived in New Jersey for 33 years, where he&nbsp;developed&nbsp;<a href="http://deansluyter.com/content/meditation-classroom"><strong>classroom meditation</strong></a>&nbsp;programs at The Pingry School and worked with inmates at Northern State Prison. He is now on the faculty of the West Coast Writers Conferences and&nbsp;is married to documentary filmmaker&nbsp;<strong><a href="http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0503502/?ref_=fn_al_nm_1">Yaffa Lerea</a></strong>.<br><br><br><br><br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3,"className":"b1db4bbe0-05d5-4dad-9b2b-666d96dcc552"} -->\n<h3 class="b1db4bbe0-05d5-4dad-9b2b-666d96dcc552">Testimonials</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>"I love this guy, especially going over on alternate Tuesdays for meditation <strong>fun</strong> <em>and</em> milk and cookies."<br><em>Some Random Santa Monica Dude</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"b1d593494-6672-46c9-9559-2d650cec462b"} -->\n<p class="b1d593494-6672-46c9-9559-2d650cec462b">"The laid-back, down-to-earth approach made meditation appealing and easy, even for complete novices.&nbsp;Deans presentation was of tremendous value in supporting our view of meditations benefits for our associates, both personal and professional."<br><em>Haley Akin, Senior Health &amp; Wellness Specialist,&nbsp;<strong>Garmin International</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"b835d64c9-bc37-49f3-b1a9-43cc42bd0e4b"} -->\n<p class="b835d64c9-bc37-49f3-b1a9-43cc42bd0e4b">"We loved having you at Timber Creek, and we\'re most grateful for what you offered. The guests soaked it up and loved your natural, genuine style. We\'re elated you could come and look forward to a future visit."<br><em>Tom Jacobs, Director,&nbsp;<strong>Timber Creek Retreat House</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":345,"align":"left","width":292,"height":195,"className":"b2817f801-be4b-4d3c-857e-0c02066a0612"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-image b2817f801-be4b-4d3c-857e-0c02066a0612"><figure class="alignleft is-resized"><img src="http://wp.deansluyter.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Garmin.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-345" width="292" height="195"/><figcaption><em>Dean speaking to engineers at Garmin International</em></figcaption></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"be315014a-1099-4dd4-b631-5ba08f64077a"} -->\n<p class="be315014a-1099-4dd4-b631-5ba08f64077a">"What a pleasure to host Dean for his Natural Meditation workshop! Dean speaks with clarity and ease from his own years of experience with meditation, so students are naturally engaged. He made a connection with everyone in the room  from seasoned yogis to my skeptical 70-year-old mother!"<br><em>Jamie Rye, owner,&nbsp;<strong>One Tree Yoga,&nbsp;</strong>Omaha</em>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"bae481728-32ff-47d1-8026-13f027c2598a"} -->\n<p class="bae481728-32ff-47d1-8026-13f027c2598a">"Dean\'s methodology is simple and easy to grasp. He is practical in his teachings and is a presenter who is easy to warm up to."<br><em>Jos Falla, Guatemala Education Officer,&nbsp;<strong>Young Presidents\' Organization</strong></em>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"b8d087d42-5188-4c61-97ce-5147d756a70d"} -->\n<p class="b8d087d42-5188-4c61-97ce-5147d756a70d">"You made killers peaceful."<br><em>Meditation Program Participant,&nbsp;<strong>Northern State Prison,&nbsp;</strong>Newark, NJ</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3,"className":"b53670fef-33fd-4a08-9fea-52bd91cb38f1"} -->\n<h3 class="b53670fef-33fd-4a08-9fea-52bd91cb38f1">Teachers</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"b6bd96326-1d98-4a39-8ddf-7770e1a4a15c"} -->\n<p class="b6bd96326-1d98-4a39-8ddf-7770e1a4a15c">Dean is deeply grateful to the many teachers who have guided him over the years, representing methods and traditions including Advaita Vedanta, Bhakti Yoga, Transcendental Meditation, Umbanda, and Vajrayana Buddhism. Teachers whose personal guidance has been especially important include Maharishi Mahesh Yogi, Charles Genoud, Mooji, and Rupert Spira.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About Dean', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '92-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-05-21 00:53:23', '2019-05-21 00:53:23', '', 92, 'http://wp.deansluyter.com/92-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
